    <string name="trace_fix_hns_stale">Let HNS sync catch up, then retry. The local proof is valid for its historical block, but not current enough to decide whether the name exists now.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_hns_unavailable">Sync headers/proofs first, then retry. No verified HNS proof was available.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_add_delegation" translatable="false">Add usable HNS delegation data: NS plus GLUE4/GLUE6 or SYNTH4/SYNTH6. To work without port 53, add a proof-anchored hnsdns=1 authoritative DoH declaration to the HNS resource.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_port53_interception" translatable="false">This network returned a DNS reply for a non-routable TEST-NET destination, which confirms transparent port 53 interception. Use authoritative DoH; the HNS owner must publish a proof-anchored hnsdns=1 endpoint so the browser can bootstrap it without DNS.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_doh_answered" translatable="false">Direct authoritative DNS on port 53 failed, but the authoritative DoH endpoint answered and validated.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_nameserver_unreliable_with_doh" translatable="false">Your delegated nameserver candidate did not answer reliably. Keep authoritative DNS reachable on UDP/TCP 53 and publish proof-anchored hnsdns=1 bootstrap metadata for networks that intercept or block port 53.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_nameserver_unreliable">Your delegated nameserver candidate did not answer reliably. Ensure authoritative DNS is reachable on UDP 53 and TCP 53.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_dnssec_bogus">Fix the delegated DNSSEC chain: HNS DS must match child DNSKEY, signatures must be current, and denial data must be valid.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_dnssec_before_tlsa">Fix delegated DNSSEC first. TLSA/DANE was not evaluated because secure resolution failed before the TLSA lookup.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_renew_cert">Renew the origin HTTPS certificate. The gateway reached an HTTPS origin, but TLS failed because the certificate is past its validity window.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_origin_address_missing">Serve A/AAAA for the requested host from delegated DNS. HNS GLUE/SYNTH data is only used to reach nameservers, not as the origin address.</string>
    <string name="trace_fix_compat_fallback_used">Compatibility DoH fallback was used. Enable Strict HNS mode to verify whether the site works fully without third-party DoH.</string>
